high_descs: Go right and then turn to the left to face the spoon on the white table.
Pick up the spoon from the table.
Cross the room to stand in front of the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick up the spoon.
Turn around and cross the room to stand at the white table.
Put the spoon on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean spoon on a table.

high_descs: Move to the right side of the dining table ahead of you
Pick up the scoop from the table
Move to the sink to the left of you
Clean scoop in the sink with water and pick up
Move to the table to the right of you
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned scoop on the dining table.

high_descs: Walk around the table to face the spoon on the opposite side.
Pick up the ladle on the table.
Turn around and walk across the room towards the left to face the sink.
Wash the ladle in the sink and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the spot where the ladle was originally.
Place the ladle on the table in it's original spot.
anns.task_desc: To wash as ladle as well as return it to where it came from.
